WEBVTT

00:07:31.442 --> 00:07:33.678
They demolish them and evict them

00:07:33.702 --> 00:07:37.448
and move them away
from their cities and economies

00:07:37.472 --> 00:07:39.995
in order to build a new infrastructure.

00:07:41.456 --> 00:07:44.099
They move them into vertical housing,

00:07:45.234 --> 00:07:47.879
which in reality looks like this.

00:07:48.982 --> 00:07:50.782
Now when built in high densities,

00:07:50.806 --> 00:07:52.744
they lack natural light and ventilation,

00:07:52.768 --> 00:07:55.206
and it often leads
to unhealthy conditions.

00:07:56.815 --> 00:07:58.702
Now, on one hand,

00:07:58.726 --> 00:08:02.218
poor people are not involved
